thread.title: BRIEF-Shandong Yisheng Livestock & Poultry Breeding sees FY 2018 Q1 net profit up 194.26 pct to 241.34 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Shandong Yisheng Livestock & Poultry Breeding sees FY 2018 Q1 net profit up 194.26 pct to 241.34 pct

organizations.name: shandong yisheng livestock & poultry breeding co ltd

text:
March 6(Reuters) - Shandong Yisheng Livestock & Poultry Breeding Co Ltd :
* Sees FY 2018 Q1 net profit to increase by 194.26 percent to 241.34 percent, or to be 10 million yuan to 11.6 million yuan
* Says FY 2017 Q1 net profit was 3.4 million yuan
* The reason for the forecast is increased sales price of commercial chicken Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/aGB2on Further company coverage: (Beijing Headline News)
